description:
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic medicines optimisation technician to join the team at Horton Rehabilitation Services. Horton Rehabilitation Services comprises of four units within sprawling therapeutic grounds in Epsom, Surrey. These include High Dependency Units as well as community inpatient rehabilitation services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will support and enhance the clinical care of patients within Horton Rehabilitation Services. They will be responsible for the provision of pharmacy services, providing a high quality, efficient service to patients residing at Horton Rehabilitation Services. They will also ensure that pharmacy technical operations (handling and storage of medicines) are undertaken in a safe, secure and efficient manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSara SazanJob titleSpecialist Mental Health PharmacistEmail addressssazan@hotmail.comTelephone number07802865854&lt;/p&gt;
